Package: tidyplastic
Title: Tools for Analyzing Plastic Waste Cleanup Efficiency
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Rayan", "Tahir", email = "you@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to load, clean, and visualize
    the Break Free From Plastic audit dataset from Tidy Tuesday
    (2021, Week 5). Supports analysis of cleanup efficiency by
    region, volunteer participation, and GDP per capita.
